            <milestone unit="line" n="1"/>An Isidô[ros, den 
            <term target="basilikosgrammateus">Königlichen] Schreiber</term> des 
            Hêrakleidês-Bezirks des Arsinoïtês,
            <milestone unit="line" n="3" rend="break"/>von Sôtelês, Sohn des Iôsêpos, des Sohnes des Theomnas, 
            und der Mutter Erôtion, aus dem Dorf [A]pollônias.
            <milestone unit="line" n="6" rend="break"/>Mein Sohn I[ôs]êpos, Sohn der Sarra, minderjährig, noch nicht 
            ausgeschieden (aus der Gruppe der Minderjährigen und überführt) zur 
            <term target="laographia">Kopfsteuer</term>, ist 
            gestorben im Monat Tybi des gegenwärtigen vierten Jahres des Traianus Caesar, des 
            Herren. <milestone unit="line" n="11"/>Hiermit bitte ich darum, daß er 
            <term target="taxistonteteleutekoton">unter die Verstorbenen</term> 
            aufgenommen wird.
            <milestone unit="line" n="13" rend="break"/>(2. Hand) An den 
            <term target="komogrammateus">Dorfschreiber</term>. Wenn er gestorben ist, dann 
            <app type="BGU"><lem>registriere</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">BL VIII, S. 40</bibl></wit></app> (ihn) und 
            <app type="BGU"><lem>gib</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">BL IX, S. 25</bibl></wit></app> (darüber) eine eidliche handschriftliche 
            Erklärung ab, wie üblich.
            <milestone unit="line" n="14" rend="break"/>Im 4. Jahr des Imperator Caesar Nerva Traian[us] Augustus Germanicus 
            am <app type="BGU+DDbDP"><lem>16.</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">BGU IV 1068; Chrest. Wilck. 62; CPJ II 427</bibl></wit></app> 
            Mecheir.
            <milestone unit="line" n="18" rend="break"/>(3. Hand) Ich, der oben genannte Sôtelês, 
            Sohn des Iôsêpos, schwöre beim Imperator Caesa[r <app type="BGU+DDbDP"><lem>Nerva] Traian[us Optimus] 
                Augustus [Germanicus]</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">PACKMANN, ZPE 89, 1991, S. 101 f.</bibl></wit></app> 
            <gap reason="illegible" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
        </p></div><div n="tran.9450" type="translation" lang="en" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>
            <milestone unit="line" n="1"/>To Isido[ros], <term target="basilikosgrammateus">royal scribe</term> 
            of the Arsinoite nome, Themistos division,
            <milestone unit="line" n="3" rend="break"/>from Soteles, son of Josepos, the son of Theomnas, mother Erotion, 
            from the village of Apollonias.
            <milestone unit="line" n="6" rend="break"/>My son J[os]epos, mother Sarra, a minor, who had not yet ceased (to 
            be a minor) with respect to the <term target="laographia">poll-tax</term>, died in the month of Tybi of the present 
            fourth year of Traianus Caesar, the lord. <milestone unit="line" n="11"/>Therefore I request that he is 
            included amongst <term target="taxistonteteleutekoton">those, who have died</term>.
            <milestone unit="line" n="13" rend="break"/>(m. 2) To the 
            <term target="komogrammateus">village scribe</term>. If he died, 
            <app type="BGU"><lem>register</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">BL VIII 40</bibl></wit></app> him and <app type="BGU"><lem>make a report with a 
                written sworn statement</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">BL IX 25</bibl></wit></app>, as usual.
            <milestone unit="line" n="15" rend="break"/>Year 4 of Imperator Caesar Nerva Traianus Augustus Germanicus, 
            Mecheir <app type="BGU+DDbDP"><lem>16</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">BGU IV 1068; Chrest. Wilck. 62; CPJ II 427</bibl></wit></app>.
            <milestone unit="line" n="18" rend="break"/>(m. 3) I, Soteles, son of Josepos, the above 
            mentioned, swear by Imperator Caesa[r <app type="BGU+DDbDP"><lem>Nerva] Traian[us Optimus] Augustus 
                [Germanicus]</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">Packmann, ZPE 89, 1991, 101-102</bibl></wit></app> <gap reason="illegible" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
        </p></div></body></text></TEI.2>